I Visited Om Sai Dental Clinic for my Root Canal Treatment, and Met Dr. Rahul The first time. though the Root canal was chronic and had tremendous Pain but Dr. Rahul Did treat it painlessly, the best thing about Dr. Rahul is he first makes his patient very comfortable. also the other best thing is he will never advise his patient anything which is unwanted. i suggest once you should visit Om sai Dental Clinic and i bet Dr. Rahul will become your family dentist then.

wish you all the success in you carrier.

Dr. Rahul explains everything in detail and would suggest the right treatment with you. Won't unnecessarily get things complicated. My treatment is still going on, and the experience has been very good. Though the clinic is far from my place, this remains as my most preferred dental clinic in Mumbai.

Dr. Rahul is an excellent dentist. My visit was very pleasant. It was my first time there, everyone was nice and very caring and nothing but smiling faces. I’ve had done root canal on one teeth and Dr. Rahul explained everything he was going to do in terms that I could even understand. He also educated me on how to properly brush my teeth. Their prices are reasonable for a downtown office. I highly recommend Om Dental Clinic.
